{"tid":2447624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好憎自己 點解咁懦弱 點解每次都冇勇氣","createTime":"2021-03-15T10:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T10:07:16.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d559ff6925bbca4b6229c778afbe141fd9853a03","tid":2447624,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"每次行樓梯上巴士上層個心速都會加速<br />\n期待自己係有選擇權既人<br />\n而唔係滿懷期待最終失望既人<br />\n今日我又走上上層<br />\n又係好多一個人既乘客<br />\n遠處見到有個自己坐緊既靚女禁緊電話<br />\n雖然我內心好希望可以坐佢旁邊享受接下來一個鐘既車程<br />\n但我真係冇勇氣我好驚人地當我係變態<br />\n點解咁多空位 偏偏要坐我隔離？<br />\n如事者已經一年<br />\n而我每次既鄰座都係煙剷地盤肥鳩大叔🚬"},{"pid":"7e3ee4722e38531f6c4d7845e07eb068e95907cc","tid":2447624,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"身有屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8057e18e86e2f834cddc83edb5badd56cbe330af","tid":2447624,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHCbG5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHCbG5g.jpg&h=ac15a16b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39052782335c32bd0ccef6b6b67adbf13dfccbb3","tid":2447624,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T10:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}